Adding the `handleMagic` function and the "MAGIC" button.
The function utilizes the Clipboard API to read (preferring HTML to keep formatting), processes the content immediately, updates the UI, and writes the result back to the clipboard using the smart copy logic (HTML + Plain Text).

```typescript
